::Magmatron/CyberShark::

    "Mantella false alarm, Bobertron and Bazooka please return to base." 
Magmatron said into his comm. 
    "Sir, I have met a Transformer, she appears to be upset about something, 
allow me a few more minutes to see if I can calm her." CyberShark said back.
    "Very well, tell her that Magmatron wishes her the best." Magmatron said.
